'''甘氨酸盐酸盐'''是一种化合物，化学式为C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>6</sub>ClNO<sub>2</sub>。它可由[[甘氨酸|甘氨酸]]和[[盐酸|盐酸]]反应得到。<ref name=Liwschitz>{{cite journal|journal=The Journal of Organic Chemistry|volume=21|issue=12|language=en|issn=0022-3263|date=1956-12|pages=1530–1530|doi=10.1021/jo01118a614|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/jo01118a614|title=Notes - A New Method for the Preparation of Hydrochlorides (hydrobromides) of Amino Acids|accessdate=2020-08-24|author=Y. Liwschitz, A. Zikhs, I. Shahak}}</ref>它和甲醇或乙醇在[[氯化亚砜|氯化亚砜]]的存在下反应，可以得到[[甘氨酸甲酯盐酸盐|甘氨酸甲酯盐酸盐]]<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Polymer Chemistry|volume=7|issue=21|language=en|issn=1759-9954|date=2016|pages=3509–3519|doi=10.1039/C6PY00515B|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=C6PY00515B|title=N-Ester-substituted polyacrylamides with a tunable lower critical solution temperature (LCST): the N-ester-substitute dependent thermoresponse|accessdate=2020-08-24|author=Shengli Chen, Yuan Zhang, Ke Wang, Heng Zhou, Wangqing Zhang}}</ref>或甘氨酸乙酯盐酸盐<ref>Imrei, Lajos; Gajari, Antal; Hidasi, Gyorgy; Szatmari, Ede; Rozsa, Laszlo; Magdanyi, Laszlo; Nagy, Lajos. Process for producing glycine ethyl ester hydrochloride. 1993. HU 61521 A2.</ref>。它在乙酸中的热饱和溶液和[[甘氨酸|甘氨酸]]降温结晶，可以得到[[:d:Q27252538|双甘氨酸单盐酸盐]]（C<sub>4</sub>H<sub>11</sub>ClN<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>，CAS 7490-95-1）。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=64|issue=6|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=1942-06|pages=1286–1287|doi=10.1021/ja01258a014|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja01258a014|title=Bis(Amino Acid) Derivatives. I. Diglycine 1 Halogen Acid Addition Products|accessdate=2020-08-24|author=Walter S. Frost}}</ref>

